title: THE_HITPACK_vol_1-First digital comic!.zip
description:
HITPACK is a new way of reading comics. Here's why: 
- 30 comic pages.

- The page size is 1024x768, so that means for you NO SCROLLING OR ZOOMING whatsoever. It just

fits your computer screen.

- High resolution images where you can appreciate all the page details.

- Confortable for reading font size.

- Loads of extra and bonus materials: Pin-ups, sketches, pencil pages...

- Interactive easy to navigate menus.

- Lots of creative possibilities.
